high_descs: Turn right, then right again and face the counter with the bread on top in front of you.
Pick up the cup from the counter in front of you.
Turn around and turn left to face the microwave above the stove in front of you.
Heat up the cup in the microwave in front of you and take in out.
Turn around and face the fridge to your right.
Place the cup in the fridge and close it.
anns.task_desc: Place a hot cup in the fridge.

high_descs: Turn right and cross the room then hang right and cross the room to the couch
Pick up the black cup that is sitting on the counter
Turn around and cross the room to the counter then turn left and go to the stove
Open the microwave that is above the stove and place the cup inside then close the door and turn it on.  Open the microwave again and pick up the cup and close the door.
Turn around and head towards the counter, then hang and right and walk to the fridge
Open the fridge and place the cup on the bottom shelf to the right then close the door
anns.task_desc: Place a heated cup into a fridge

high_descs: Turn right, hang a right around the edge of the counter and turn right to walk to the counter across the room.
Pick up the black glass in front of the salt shaker.
Turn around, hang a left at the counter and walk to the stove ahead.
Place the glass inside the microwave above the stove, heat it for a few seconds, remove it and close the door.
Turn around and walk towards the black fridge on the right.
Put the glass on the bottom right shelf inside the fridge and close the door.
anns.task_desc: Place a heated glass in a fridge.
